description: This study reports the identification of mosquito whole-body protein extracted using two methods: a conventional approach based on TCA/Acetone precipitation by following a method by Wang et al., (2015) and a commercial method based on formulated protein extraction reagent Cytobuster (Sigma, Germany). The resultant protein fragment was analyzed using QTOF ESI  LCMS/MS.
